org.checkerframework.framework.type

Class HashcodeAtmVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.checkerframework.framework.type.visitor.AnnotatedTypeScanner<R,P>
      • org.checkerframework.framework.type.visitor.SimpleAnnotatedTypeScanner<Integer,Void>
        • org.checkerframework.framework.type.HashcodeAtmVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnnotatedTypeVisitor<Integer,Void>

    public class HashcodeAtmVisitor
extends SimpleAnnotatedTypeScanner<Integer,Void>
    Computes the hashcode of an AnnotatedTypeMirror using the underlying type and primary annotations and the hash code of component types of AnnotatedTypeMirror.

    This class should be synchronized with EqualityAtmComparer.

    See Also:
    for more details.

    This is used by AnnotatedTypeMirror.hashcode.
